text: The China lady who serves me is very friendly and helpful after I did some translation for her from a young Indian lady cause they could not understand each other. The noodles 🍜  was not the best but could be improved upon as the fishballs and fishcakes were run of the mill factory made type, hope that changes will be made so that it could stand out from the other fishballs noodles stalls. I will be back to try their laksa and lor mee. 💪💪💪
If bad if you want a simple bowl of noodles! It's great when I'm not sure of what to eat. Portion size is just nice as well!
5.80 after 10% discount. yet prawn from prawn noodle is not even fresh and shells are not peeled off! I rather pay cheaper price and go elsewhere, at least the small prawns are peeled.
